title: Andrew W.K. Close Calls With Brick Walls US Vinyl Bonus Tracks
description:
These are the 5 bonus tracks from the US vinyl release of Andrew W.K.'s Close Calls With Brick Walls (2007).  They are ONLY available on the vinyl edition and I have not seen them available for download anywhere else.  I ripped them myself from the vinyl with professional digital equipment so they are CD quality.  They are mp3 files at 128 kbps in full stereo sound.  Here is the song information:

1. Big Party - 2:43
2. We're Not Gunna Get Old - 4:55
3. Kicks And Bricks - 2:55
4. I've Got Know Fear - 3:25
5. We Will Boogie - 2:40
(6. Untitled Moaning sounds after the end of We Will Boogie - 1:34)
